elements.name: Crear y publicar varios posts, verificar su visibilidad en la lista y validar contenido

steps.name: I open the Ghost login page
I am on the posts list page
I create a new post with title "My New Post 1" and content "This is the content of my first post"
I create a new post with title "My New Post 2" and content "This is the content of my second post"
I should see all posts in the posts list with titles:
I open the post with title "My New Post 1"
I should see the post title "My New Post 1" and content "This is the content of my first post"
I go back to the posts list page
I open the post with title "My New Post 2"
I should see the post title "My New Post 2" and content "This is the content of my second post"
